title JM Family ITSM Chatbot - High-Level System Architecture

// Top-level network boundary
Intranet Network [color: blue, icon: shield] {
  // Frontend group

  // AI processing
  Azure OpenAI [icon: azure-openai]

  // Knowledge base
  SharePoint [icon: sharepoint]

  // Ticketing system
  ServiceNow [icon: servicenow]
}

// External user (not in intranet)

// Connections
Azure OpenAI > SharePoint: retrieve knowledge
Azure OpenAI > ServiceNow: manage tickets

// Security notes
// All connections within Intranet Network are secured via HTTPS and private endpoints


